{"tid":593785,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無人空中的士將於新西蘭測試","createTime":"2018-03-15T09:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T13:51:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f450975bc205100dc49d8dbd32972b3b011f3a81","tid":593785,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:32:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180315/20332388\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180315%2F20332388&d=TJ3MZuC4%2BvlQOXGaWtZ5AQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=a006719d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180315%2F20332388&h=732c4d0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180315/20332388</a><br />\n<br />\n無人空中的士將於新西蘭測試<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180315/large/a1703a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180315%2Flarge%2Fa1703a.gif&h=7ee8bae6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佩奇（小圖）的「空中的士」公司推出無人駕駛機Cora。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGoogle創辦人之一佩奇（Larry Page）投資的無人空中的士計劃，前日獲新西蘭當局發牌批准測試研發，旗下公司稱有望革新個人運輸系統。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n垂直升降　時速150公里<br />\n<br />\n佩奇創辦的科技公司Kitty Hawk屬下的Zephyr Airworks公司，獲發牌批准測試名為「Cora」的電動飛行器。Zephyr行政總裁里德（Fred Reid）表示：「我們提供零污染、零排放的可靠飛行載具，我們認為這是運輸系統革新的下一步。」<br />\n<br />\n每架Cora可載兩人，翼展11米，飛行時速達150公里，最長飛行距離100公里，可在900米高空飛行。它的兩翼上設有12組旋翼，可讓Cora如直升機般垂直升降，但據研發團隊指Cora遠比直升機安靜，意味可利用市內建築物屋頂、停車場作為升降坪。<br />\n<br />\n團隊將於新西蘭南島測試Cora模型機，機上將搭載3台獨立運作的電腦，每部會各自計算飛行路線以確保安全，萬一有意外會放出降落傘。Zephyr指出，公司無意出售Cora，一旦投入服務公眾須要預約，模式相似電召的士程式Uber。<br />\n<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"79d0d8347db2158bd6849069990f77099805a00c","tid":593785,"uid":142405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:04:00.000Z","msg":"香港快d引入 唔使再睇的士狗面色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8719aa62c72de7593947c638d16e54aff624d316","tid":593785,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79d0d8347db2158bd6849069990f77099805a00c","tid":593785,"uid":142405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:04:00.000Z","msg":"香港快d引入 唔使再睇的士狗面色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:47:31.000Z","msg":"到時咪又會拒載、呢度嗰度唔停得"},{"pid":"5e42a0dd422902ecec4c4f5ec2859a73e9556883","tid":593785,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79d0d8347db2158bd6849069990f77099805a00c","tid":593785,"uid":142405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:04:00.000Z","msg":"香港快d引入 唔使再睇的士狗面色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:49:06.000Z","msg":"睇CX同AAHK面色囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n民航處唔知喇"},{"pid":"4c6506df769a87df2d14680b8705bf5a43dbc5b4","tid":593785,"uid":137551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:51:04.000Z","msg":"建築物屋頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港已經無可能引入"}]}